---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import RemittancePage from '../../components/RemittancePage.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Send Money from Brazil to USA — BRL to USD Transfer Guide"
  description="Complete guide to sending money from Brazil to the United States. Compare BRL to USD exchange rates, fees, and top remittance services for fast, secure transfers to the US."
  keywords="Brazil to USA remittance, BRL to USD, send money Brazil United States, Brazil US money transfer, BRL USD exchange rate, enviar dinheiro Brasil EUA, Brazilian diaspora USA"
  image="https://images.pexels.com/photos/290386/pexels-photo-290386.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200&h=630&fit=crop"
  type="website"
>
  <RemittancePage
    flag="🇺🇸"
    countryEn="United States"
    countryZh="美国"
    currencyCode="USD"
    currencyNameEn="US Dollar"
    currencyNameZh="美元"
    rate="0.17 USD"
    externalHref="https://www.pandaremit.com/en/bra/send-money-to-unitedstates"
    heroImage="https://images.pexels.com/photos/290386/pexels-photo-290386.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600&h=600&fit=crop"
    overviewEn="The United States hosts the largest Brazilian diaspora community outside Brazil, with approximately 1.8 million Brazilians living across states like Florida, Massachusetts, New York, and California. Sending money from Brazil to the US is one of the most common international transfer corridors, used for everything from supporting family members to paying tuition fees and covering living expenses. The BRL-USD corridor is well-served by both traditional banks and modern digital remittance platforms, with competitive rates and reliable delivery."
    overviewZh="美国拥有巴西境外最大的巴西侨民社区，约有180万巴西人生活在佛罗里达、马萨诸塞、纽约和加利福尼亚等州。从巴西向美国汇款是最常见的国际转账走廊之一，用途涵盖支持家庭成员、支付学费和支付生活费等。雷亚尔-美元走廊由传统银行和现代数字汇款平台提供良好服务，汇率具竞争力且交付可靠。"
    tip1En="Compare total cost: The exchange rate margin is often more significant than the flat fee. A service with no fees but a wide rate spread can cost more overall."
    tip1Zh="比较总成本：汇率差价通常比固定手续费更重要。没有手续费但汇率差价较大的服务，总成本可能更高。"
    tip2En="Time your transfers: The BRL/USD rate fluctuates daily. Setting up rate alerts on digital platforms helps you send when the rate is favorable."
    tip2Zh="把握汇款时机：雷亚尔/美元汇率每日波动。在数字平台上设置汇率提醒有助于您在汇率有利时汇款。"
    tip3En="Declare large transfers: Brazil requires declaration of transfers above $10,000 USD equivalent through the Banco Central do Brasil's system. Ensure compliance to avoid delays."
    tip3Zh="申报大额转账：巴西要求通过巴西中央银行系统申报超过1万美元等值的转账。确保合规以避免延误。"
    communityEn="The Brazilian community in the US is concentrated in Greater Boston, Miami, New York City, and Northern New Jersey. Known for their entrepreneurial spirit, many Brazilians in the US own businesses, work in construction, hospitality, and healthcare, and regularly send remittances to family in Brazil. Cultural organizations and Catholic churches serve as community hubs."
    communityZh="在美巴西社区主要集中在大波士顿、迈阿密、纽约市和北新泽西州。以创业精神著称，许多在美巴西人拥有企业，在建筑、酒店和医疗行业工作，并定期向巴西家人汇款。文化组织和天主教堂是社区枢纽。"
    regulatoryEn="Transfers from Brazil to the US are regulated by Banco Central do Brasil. For transfers above R$10,000, documentation of the transfer purpose is required. US anti-money laundering regulations also apply on the receiving end. Using licensed remittance services ensures compliance with both Brazilian and US regulations."
    regulatoryZh="从巴西到美国的转账受巴西中央银行监管。超过10,000雷亚尔的转账需要提供转账目的的文件证明。美国反洗钱法规也适用于接收端。使用持牌汇款服务可确保符合巴西和美国的法规要求。"
    transferTime="1–2 days"
    minAmount="R$50"
    maxAmount="R$50,000"
  />
</Layout>
